author: hwright
msg: (1.5.3) Bring up-to-date with revisions merged to 1.5.x.

author: hwright
msg: ra_serf: Fix the svn_ra_replay API, which got broken when svn_ra_replay_range
was added. This API is not used anymore in svnsync. Bug was reported and fix
There's a small trailing whitespace conflict during merge.

author: hwright
msg: Fix issue #3285 - 'svn log -g' mistakes property change for
r33136 adds the regression test.  r33137 is the fix.

author: hwright
msg: po-update.sh: Search for messages in svn_fs_util.h.
po-update.sh without this change doesn't add messages from svn_fs_util.h
to .po files, so these messages are untranslated.

author: hwright
msg: Fix a bug whereby 'svn mv' could cause the client to loop forever.
Justification: hanging forever while memory grows is double-plus ungood.
